    <h3 id="jump">Story 2.1.1: <a href="../Bonus/1_Homeward Rambles.php">Homeward Rambles</a></h3>
    <p><b>Economic:</b> The coming new year brings mixed conversation about where to place resources.  Building in the caverns is very important to creating a true settled home for the people, however there is a discussion about waiting for more research to happen so that things go as smoothly as possible.  This would mean putting resources back into the land around the Hilt’Inn - fixing up the outlying huts and maybe attempting to figure out what to grow out there as a food source for the visitors that may not...live on a diet of small animals, large bugs, and mushrooms.  Eventually, they come to the agreement to start the cavern settlement first because echos be damned they really want to get back into a habitat they are familiar with.</p>
    <p><i>Establishment</i> trapping of <b>Infrastructure</b> (upgrade use)</p>
