    <p><b>Political:</b> *<i>sing song voice</i>*  Cloak and dagger!  In all seriousness, getting a routine in place is not a bad idea and is actually giving the scouts a rotating schedule, which is helping with a returning sense of normalcy.  With Shyrendora and Amenidal’s return, news of The Tourist is spread far and wide.  Shyrendora informs everyone that if she is discovered to not engage in a hostile way, just come find her.  Everyone also learns that Amenidal told people to come visit...though he was rather vague about where the visitors should come to.  Keeping an eye out does not seem like a terrible thing.</p>
